column2: select my.*,SpecPhotoAll.*, galSpecExtra.*, galSpecIndx.*, galSpecInfo.*, galSpecLine.*   into mydb.HSC_SDSS_cat   from mydb.HSC_SDSS as my     JOIN SpecPhotoAll on my.id = SpecPhotoAll.objID     left join galSpecExtra on galSpecExtra.specObjID = SpecPhotoAll.specObjID     left join galSpecIndx on galSpecIndx.specObjID = SpecPhotoAll.specObjID     left join galSpecInfo on galSpecInfo.specObjID = SpecPhotoAll.specObjID     left join galSpecLine on galSpecLine.specObjID = SpecPhotoAll.specObjID
